flowchart TD
    A[Customer discovers BhumiSeva] --> B{How?}
    B -->|Google Search| C[Lands on Homepage]
    B -->|WhatsApp Referral| C
    B -->|Social Media Ad| C

    C --> D[Browses Services]
    D --> E[Opens Service Detail Page]
    E --> F[Fills Multi-Step Enquiry Form]

    F --> G{Step 1: Personal Info}
    G -->|Name, Phone, City| H{Step 2: Service Details}
    H -->|Khesra, District, etc.| I[Submits Lead]

    I --> J[Lead saved to Database]
    J --> K[Customer gets WhatsApp confirmation]
    K --> L[BhumiSeva team calls within 2hrs]

    L --> M{Payment}
    M -->|Online| N[Razorpay Checkout]
    M -->|Cash| O[Pay on delivery]

    N --> P[Payment confirmed]
    O --> P

    P --> Q[Document Processing Starts]
    Q --> R[Status: In Progress]
    R --> S[Document Ready]
    S --> T[Delivery - Digital + Physical]
    T --> U[Customer leaves Review]

    style A fill:#065A82,color:#fff
    style I fill:#028090,color:#fff
    style N fill:#02C39A,color:#fff
